1
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:06,000
National Radio and Television Administration

2
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:41,400
Mom, you might have misunderstood Liu Wei.

3
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:45,160
I've failed as a mother.

4
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,039
Mom, what do you mean by that?

5
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,240
Qin Gang.

6
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,840
When will you finally grow up?

7
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,240
Mom, don't get upset.

8
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:00,940
I'm already a father. How can you say I haven't grown up?

9
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,760
This is my fault.

10
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:10,259
I raised you by myself since you were little.

11
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,330
I was afraid of letting you suffer.

12
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:16,840
So I've always spoiled you.

13
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:22,760
Food, clothes, expenses, education, everything...

14
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:24,940
I gave you the best of everything.

15
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:28,620
I just hoped you wouldn't fall behind at the starting line.

16
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:33,760
And you didn't lose at the starting line.

17
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,280
You're still standing at the starting line.

18
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,680
You never even moved.

19
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:42,840
I gave you money to open a car dealership.

20
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,970
But what have you made of it?

21
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,560
Although it hasn't gone bankrupt...

22
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,480
It's barely surviving.

23
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,240
But that's not the point.

24
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,460
The point is...

25
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:58,200
I failed to instill a sense of responsibility in you.

26
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:05,920
Xiao Gang, I can't be with you forever.

27
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,560
If you don't wake up now, it will be too late.

28
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:13,480
Really, I'm afraid that one day...

29
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,410
Between you and Xiaobao...

30
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,760
The father won't act like a father, and the son won't act like a son.

31
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,800
He'll hate you and resent you.

32
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:23,040
Just like how you resent and hate your father.

33
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,100
Do you understand?

34
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,329
That's impossible.

35
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,760
Xiaobao is my own son.

36
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:33,240
Xiao Gang, I don't have time...

37
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:36,770
To struggle with you anymore. Do you understand?

38
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,640
Let me be honest with you.

39
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:44,000
The American doctors have given me their verdict.

40
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,700
I only have three months left.

41
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:52,160
Mom, you're just trying to scare me, right?

42
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,620
I'm telling you the truth.

43
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:01,720
Mom.

44
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,840
Those doctors are talking nonsense.

45
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,100
We won't believe them.

46
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,840
Science is so advanced nowadays.

47
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:10,200
What disease can't be cured, right?

48
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,680
We don't lack money.

49
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:14,680
We'll definitely find a way to cure you.

50
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,279
This isn't a problem.

51
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,089
I'm not afraid of dying.

52
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,040
But what I worry about

53
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,320
is you.

54
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,000
Xinxin

55
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,080
and my grandson.

56
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:31,080
My only wish

57
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:34,520
is that the three of you

58
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:37,280
can live well together.

59
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,400
If that happens,

60
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,200
even if I die,

61
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:47,480
I'll be content. Do you understand?

62
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,560
It's a user-friendly design.

63
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:54,290
This will run through our entire promotion plan.

64
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,120
This will not only help you

65
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,560
clarify your product positioning.

66
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,320
It will also allow buyers

67
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,480
when purchasing the product,

68
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,360
to

69
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,440
feel our care

70
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:04,500
and thoughtfulness from head to toe.

71
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,640
I believe you three executives

72
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:09,600
now have a better understanding of our company's capabilities.

73
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,840
If there are no questions,

74
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:13,000


75
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,200
Alright, let's do it.

76
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:20,490
Mr. Shi, this contract signing went quite smoothly.

77
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,240
Thank you.

78
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,410
It's been a pleasure working with you.

79
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,440
Mr. Xu, let's celebrate together tonight.

80
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,240
No problem.

81
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,700
Excuse me for a moment.

82
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,240
Lulu.

83
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:56,320
They're too rowdy.

84
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,360
They mentioned celebrating tonight.

85
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,240
Let's go together.

86
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,960
You go have fun. I'm not going.

87
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:04,000
Do you have something else to do?

88
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,320
Don't bother me.

89
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,000
What's wrong?

90
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:11,320
We signed such an important contract today.

91
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,520
Why aren't you happy?

92
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,520
I've never felt like such a failure before.

93
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,960
How did we fail?

94
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,200
We succeeded today.

95
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,760
That was you, not us.

96
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,520
You did everything.

97
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,120
Now they all see you as the leader.

98
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,720
No. So what?

99
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,560
This company is yours.

100
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,090
No matter how well I perform, it's all for you.

101
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:36,880
I don't need that.

102
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,960
No, Lulu.

103
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:42,040
Go. Go enjoy your success.

104
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,480
Dr. Jia.

105
00:06:57,440 --> 00:07:00,040
Is my mother's condition really that serious?

106
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,840
I've been in contact with specialists in America.

107
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,160
It is indeed very serious.

108
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,420
Please do everything you can to save her.

109
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:11,040
Medical experts have already reached their conclusion.

110
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,440
I wish I could do more, but my hands are tied.

111
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,530
Let me give you some advice.

112
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:18,040
During this period, you must ensure

113
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,970
that Mr. Qin stays in good spirits.

114
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:23,920
If Mr. Qin experiences any significant emotional distress,

115
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,220
he could be in serious danger.

116
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,240
Okay.

117
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,560
Good.

118
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,240
I've reviewed all the contracts.

119
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,170
You did an excellent job this time.

120
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,640
Great.

121
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,720
Of course, I must treat you to a meal.

122
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,760
Sure. You pick the place.

123
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,160
Alright.

124
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,840
Let's leave it at that for now.

125
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:14,120
Sounds good. Bye-bye.

126
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,560
I'm sorry.

127
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,520
You haven't done anything wrong.

128
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,560
Why apologize?

129
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,360
I'm apologizing on behalf of my mother.

130
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,559
You are you, and your mother is your mother.

131
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,059
I don't need your apology.

132
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,640
Silly.

133
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,280
I know everything your mother did

134
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,480
was for your own good.

135
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,960
Although she has some misunderstandings about me,

136
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,960
I understand her.

137
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,600
That's good.

138
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,080
I came today to tell you that

139
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:57,100
my mother wants me to get back with Wan Xinxin again.

140
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,920
This time I have to take some action.

141
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,400
That's nothing new to me.

142
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,330
Isn't that what you've always been doing?

143
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:08,220
I mean I have to get serious this time.

144
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,540
My mother only has three months left.

145
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:21,680
I don't agree.

146
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,280
I know.

147
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,160
You want to pursue Wan Xinxin

148
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,320
just to get control of her property.

149
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,320
But none of that really matters.

150
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:32,240
Let your mother give her money to whoever she wants.

151
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,760
As long as we're together,

152
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:36,600
as long as we love each other, money isn't an issue.

153
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,820
You've always understood me before.

154
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,800
Could you for once

155
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:46,080
think from my perspective?

156
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,960
I'm a woman too.

157
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:51,560
I get jealous and upset too.

158
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,560
Every time I see

159
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,400
you with Wan Xinxin,

160
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,880
do you have any idea how I feel?

161
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:58,920
Don't you know?

162
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,800
We can find

163
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:03,480
the best doctors in the world to treat your mother.

164
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,280
I don't believe it's incurable.

165
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,800
Give me some time,

166
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,000
I can make her accept me again.

167
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:13,920
But I really don't want to keep pretending anymore.

168
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,120
I'm so tired.

169
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,200
I must win Wan Xinxin back.

170
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,360
I have to do this.

171
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,520
Hello?

172
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:40,740
No need to come to the office. Let's meet at the usual place.

173
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,520
Wan Xinxin.

174
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,660
Why are you here again?

175
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,370
I need to ask you for a favor.

176
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,900
I won't agree to it.

177
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,600
I'm already annoyed enough.

178
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,080
Would you please leave?

179
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,360
Can you let me finish?

180
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:13,620
How do you think my mother treats you?

181
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,560
Why bring that up?

182
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,440
I'm formally asking you

183
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,640
to remarry me.

184
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,920
Are you okay?

185
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,560
Huaming and I are about to get our marriage license.

186
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,160
No. Just go on with your life.

187
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,320
Go marry your Liu Wei.

188
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,980
Why did you ask me to come here?

189
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,560
You got your license?

190
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,440
Even if we haven't,

191
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,250
it's none of your business.

192
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:40,360
If you haven't gotten the license, then I still have a chance.

193
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,440
Even if you have,

194
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,400
I still have a chance.

195
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:44,080
You can divorce him and then remarry me.

196
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:44,600
Okay?

197
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:46,340
What are you saying, Qin Gang?

198
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:48,600
What kind of person do you think I am?

199
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,200
You come to me when you need me,

200
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,080
and when you don't,

201
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,440
you just kick me aside.

202
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,480
I really don't want to talk to you anymore.

203
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,960
Let me finish.

204
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,840
I, Qin Gang, have never begged anyone before,

205
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,840
but this time I'm truly begging you.

206
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:04,580
My mother only has three months left.

207
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,730
The doctors have given their verdict.

208
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:11,200
After three months, you'll be free.

209
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,400
Name your price, whatever you want.

210
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:17,780
Please, I'm begging you to help me. Will you?

211
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,860
Are you telling the truth?

212
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,040
Based on my assessment,

213
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:31,040
I think this company is very irregular.

214
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,800
It has obvious flaws.

215
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:35,610
The acquisition doesn't make much sense.

216
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,800
Indeed, experience counts.

217
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:42,320
You spotted so many issues from such limited information.

218
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,380
You've really put your heart into it.

219
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,760
Director Liu treats me so well.

220
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:50,480
If I, Jiang Kaiyang, don't show my gratitude,

221
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,970
how could I face myself?

222
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,960
I was right about you.

223
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:58,440
However, my opinion is exactly the opposite of yours.

224
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:01,520
I believe it's precisely because they have so many flaws

225
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:04,050
that we have the opportunity to acquire them.

226
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,280
That's true.

227
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,580
Let me kiss these little feet.

228
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:15,240
These little feet smell so nice.

229
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,600
How can they smell so good?

230
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,480
Wonderful.

231
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,940
I'm going to nibble on you.

232
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,440
Such sweet-smelling little hands.

233
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,800
And such sweet-smelling little feet too.

234
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,640
What a sweet-smelling grandson I have.

235
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,200
Auntie.

236
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,560
He smells so good.

237
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,840
I'll leave the baby here with you.

238
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,960
I'll be going now.

239
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,720
I'll come back for him later.

240
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,320
You're leaving?

241
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:42,220
I'm heading to work. I can give you a ride.

242
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,960
No need. I can go by myself.

243
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,880
No, absolutely not.

244
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,060
What's wrong with you?

245
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:52,360
I've never seen you so eager to work before.

246
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,320
Today,

247
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,500
I'm making the decisions.

248
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,920
No one is allowed to talk about leaving.

249
00:13:58,920 --> 00:13:59,640
Xinxin,

250
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:03,080
stay and keep me company, will you?

251
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:06,640
Xinxin,

252
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:09,840
it's been so long since we've all

253
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,120
been together like this.

254
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,690
You don't know how my heart has been

255
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,480
in limbo all this time.

256
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:19,600
Seeing you and the baby today,

257
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:21,120
my anxious heart

258
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,480
is finally at ease.

259
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,320
I'm just happy, that's all.

260
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:27,520
I know you've been missing Bao.

261
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,600
It's okay.

262
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,360
Bao can stay here with you.

263
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,080
I'll come back for him later.

264
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:34,040
It's not just Bao I've been missing.

265
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,320
I've missed you too.

266
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:40,720
About Mr. Liu,

267
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,000
whatever you do, don't mention

268
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,120
my sister-in-law.

269
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,060
I heard from her sister

270
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:47,120
that Huaming played her.

271
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:51,960
Her sister wants me to get revenge for her.

272
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:55,450
But think about it, I'm almost divorced from her sister.

273
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:58,920
Do I have time to care about her problems? Right?

274
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:02,920
Weren't they quite close with Huaming?

275
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:04,320
Exactly.

276
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:07,560
This Huaming is a real piece of work.

277
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:08,720
Let me tell you,

278
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:12,000
before he gets what he wants,

279
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:15,040
he's like a leech, sticks like glue,

280
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:16,840
all over the person.

281
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,570
