420
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,480
Don't go.

421
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:41,920
Huaming has broken up and gotten back together with you so many times.

422
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,160
And he never gives you a clear answer.

423
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:45,440
That's why I need to ask him face to face.

424
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:47,080
I need to get an answer.

425
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,680
Think about it. A man who

426
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:50,440
runs away on your wedding day

427
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:53,120
