430
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:00,000
He just said

431
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,520
I need to accept his past.

432
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:02,920
And his past is just

433
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:04,580
