437
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,360
That's just fate.

438
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:13,800
You two aren't meant to be together.

439
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,520
Now I see clearly.

440
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:19,250
This thing called fate is just one-sided effort.

441
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:21,840
Xinxin, listen to me.

442
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:22,360
Sis.

