487
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,600
And Auntie, I need to tell you,

488
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:17,520
I believe my decision three years ago wasn't wrong.

489
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:18,920
As a doctor,

490
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:21,280
